
Mike's Toolbox C++ software library
-----------------------------------

Essential building blocks for robust software development including:

    - Strings - Holds text or even binary data
    - Regular Expressions - String pattern matching (Perl syntax)
    - Containers:
        - List<item>
        - StringList
        - Map<key,value>
        - Hash<key,value>
        - iterators
    - Threading:
        - Mutex
        - Condition
        - Thread - supply a thread_main() function
    - Networking
        - IP addresses
        - Sockets

